      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-card-ico"><Icon name="sun" size={22} /></div>
        <strong>Energy Production</strong>
        <p>CoQ10 is the rate-limiting cofactor in the mitochondrial electron transport chain, which generates 95% of cellular ATP. Without adequate CoQ10, cells cannot produce sufficient energy, leading to fatigue, muscle weakness, and reduced exercise capacity — symptoms that accelerate with age.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
