        <strong>Antioxidant Protection</strong>
        <p>Ubiquinol (the reduced form of CoQ10) is one of the only lipid-soluble antioxidants that the body synthesizes endogenously. It regenerates vitamin E, protects LDL particles from oxidation (a key driver of atherosclerosis), and shields mitochondrial DNA from free radical damage.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-card-ico"><Icon name="flask" size={22} /></div>
